# Navigate Peptides — Site Architecture

## Navigation (Client-Specified)

Four items: **Compounds** | **Research** | **Quality** | **About**
Plus: "Request Access" CTA button.

## 1. Compounds

**Flow:** `/compounds` → `/compounds/[category]` → `/compounds/[category]/[slug]`

### Categories (7)
| Category | Slug | Color |
|----------|------|-------|
| Metabolic Research | metabolic | #2F4666 |
| Tissue Repair Research | tissue-repair | #9C843E |
| Cognitive Research | cognitive | #5E507F |
| Inflammation Research | inflammation | #4A141C |
| Cellular Research | cellular | #8E5660 |
| Dermal Research | dermal | #4A6B5F |
| Research Blends | blends | #474C50 |

### Product Detail Page (Client-Specified Structure)
1. Product name
2. Technical subtitle
3. Short scientific description (1 line)
4. Research focus (bullet points)
5. Studies available
6. Purity / COA information
7. Research-use disclaimer

Plus: vial photo with category color accent, product info panel, price/cart.

### Product Tags
- "Extended Half-Life" — for modified analogs
- "Long-Acting Profile" — alternative
- Include short technical explanation (no performance claims)

## 2. Research

Four subsections (client-specified):
| Subsection | Path | Content |
|------------|------|---------|
| Research Intelligence | /research/intelligence | Trend analysis, market insights |
| Research Library | /research/library | Deep-dive articles, guides |
| Research Framework | /research/framework | Methodology, classification |
| Emerging Research | /research/emerging | New compounds, novel mechanisms |

⚠️ All research content must be purely scientific. Processor prohibits blogs/FAQs implying human use.

