## Homepage Sections
1. Nav bar — Logo + 4 items + Request Access
2. Hero — Kicker, serif headline, body, CTAs, vial + info card
3. Research Categories — 7-card grid
4. Trust Signals — Third-Party Tested / Lab Use Only / GMP
5. Footer — 3 columns + disclaimer + copyright

