## Technical Requirements
- Next.js App Router, SSR/SSG for SEO
- WooCommerce backend (AllayPay requires it)
- WordPress admin for non-technical content updates
- Mobile-first (60%+ traffic is mobile), target <3s load
- Schema markup: Product, Article, Organization, BreadcrumbList, FAQPage
- XML sitemap, robots.txt, canonical URLs, Open Graph tags
